profile.name: Bright Lights Acquisition Corp.
profile.description: Bright Lights Acquisition Corp. is a blank check company. The company intends to effect a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus for a target business operating in the consumer products, media, entertainment, and sports sectors. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Los Angeles, California.
